  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 QR \u0d9b\u0dda\u0dad\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db8\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "From tomorrow, fuel will be released only to QR region",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Power and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera says that from tomorrow, fuel will be released from all petrol stations across the island only through the QR code.",
        "According to this, all the fuel station owners and managers are requested to issue fuel only to that area, the minister said.",
        "The Minister added that all petrol station owners and managers are requested to check the QR code on the device along with the vehicle number plate to verify the details."
      ],
